First Department,

June, 1994

(June 2, 1994) Chi Sun Fung, Appellant, v City of New York et al., Respondents and Third-Party Plaintiffs-Respondents. Ka Hon Construction Company, Inc., Third-Party Defendant-Respondent. [614 NYS2d 122]

Order, Supreme Court, New York County (Martin Schoenfeld, J.) entered on or about November 25, 1992, unanimously affirmed for the reasons stated by Schoenfeld, J., without costs and without disbursements. No opinion. Concur—Murphy, P. J., Rosenberger, Kupferman and Ross, JJ.
